Story: Speaker signs up

  As a prospective speaker
  I want to sign up for speaking
  So that I can be registered
  
  Scenario: Speaker signs up with all necessary field
  
    When prospective speaker is on signup page
    Then he can see all the input fields
    When signing up as a prospective speaker with email 'spe@ker.se'
    Then a new attendant with speaking proposal is created
    
  Scenario: Speaker signs up with another proposal
    
    Given a speaker is already registered
    When he signs up with a new proposal and the same email address
    Then the new proposal is registered to him